<h1>Greetings to MediApp, <%= @appointment.user.name %></h1>
<p>
  You have successfully booked an appointment with
  <strong>Dr. <%= @appointment.doctor.name %></strong> for
  <strong>
    <%= t('today') if @appointment.date_time.to_date == Date.today %>
    <%= t('tomorrow') if @appointment.date_time.to_date == Date.today + 1 %>
    <%= @appointment.date_time.to_datetime.strftime("%a, #{@appointment.date_time.to_date.day.ordinalize} %I:%M %p") %>
  </strong>
</p>
<p>
  To get your invoice, just follow this link: <a href="<%= @url %>" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><%= @url %></a>.
</p>
<p>Thanks for booking and have a great day!</p>